  "prompt": "Where can I buy Soju in mumbai?",
  "response": "As of my last update, you can typically find soju in specialty liquor stores, Korean grocery stores, or restaurants in Mumbai that serve Korean cuisine. Some specific places to consider include:\n\n1. **Korean Supermarkets**: Shops like \"Shin Shin\" or other Korean grocery stores may stock soju.\n  \n2. **Liquor Stores**: Larger liquor stores, especially those in neighborhoods with a more diverse population, might have it in their international liquor section.\n  \n3. **Korean Restaurants**: Restaurants such as \"Gogi\" or \"Sushi and More\" may offer soju for dine-in or sometimes for takeaway.\n\n4. **Online Retailers**: Check local online liquor delivery services, as they may offer a selection of international spirits including soju.\n\nMake sure to check the specific store or website for availability, and consider local laws regarding alcohol sales.",
